title: Hawley presses witness on ‘two-spirit people’ during testy Senate hearing

author: Heather Hunter
description: Late-night host Jimmy Kimmel is not letting Vice President JD Vance’s criticism slide. The comedian used his stage in Brooklyn to unload on Vance after the vice president mocked his ratings during a recent Fox News interview. title: Late-night host Jimmy Kimmel melts down at JD Vance for mocking his ratings

author: Ross O'Keefe
description: The White House is pulling the nomination of Brian Quintenz, whom President Donald Trump nominated as a board member and chairman of the Commodity Futures Trading Commission. A White House official confirmed the news to the Washington Examiner. The CFTC handles the U.S. derivatives markets, including option trading, and aims to promote their “integrity, resilience, […]
title: White House yanks Brian Quintenz nomination to head Commodity Futures Trading Commission

author: Heather Hunter
description: Late-night host Jimmy Fallon says his program is meant to entertain, not to divide, and he has no plans to change that. During an appearance on CNBC’s Squawk on the Street this week, the Tonight Show host said his monologues are designed to reach a wide audience. “Our show’s never really been that political,” Fallon […]
title: Jimmy Fallon defends show as nonpartisan: ‘We try to make everybody laugh’
